    "shortDescription": "<p>You transform the physical makeup of a weapon as you desire.</p><p>This spell functions like <i>greater magic weapon</i>, except that it subtly alters the physical properties of a weapon, enabling it to bypass damage reduction of one the following types: bludgeoning, cold iron, piercing, silver, or slashing. The affected weapon still inflicts damage of its normal type and its hardness and hit points are unchanged. This spell can be cast on a natural weapon or unarmed strike.</p>"
